+  // buffer holds the LAST reply, so we require both the command id AND the
+  // echoed slot index to match, and treat firmware's PENDING marker (status
+  // 0xFE) as "keep waiting"; (2) USB stalls - slot save/activate performs a
+  // flash sector erase with interrupts off, so reads can throw briefly;
